* Tips & Tricks

Generate a coverage output:

	$ go test -coverprofile=cov.out [package]

Generate a heat-map output:

	$ go test -covermode=count -coverprofile=cov.out [package]

View a coverage file:

	$ go tool cover -html=cov.out
